This directory contains a template for a software requirements specification, written in Latex. To build a PDF version of the document, type 'make'.

To make a dvi or postscript version, type 'make dvi' or 'make ps', respectively.

To clean up all of the files, type 'make clean'. This will leave the generated PDF, ps, and/or dvi file, but clear away all other files generated by latex. The additionally remove the PDF, ps and dvi files, type 'make CLEAN'. If there alreadty exists a compiled output file, then make will quit without saving over the output file.
